Adapter class that provides empty implementations of IDeck.

Game
Represents the main game logic of "Cincuentazo".
ICard
Represents the basic behavior of any playing card in the game "Cincuentazo".
IDeck
Interface that defines the basic behavior of any deck used in the game.

Exception thrown when a player attempts to make an invalid move.

Interface that defines the basic behavior of a player in the "Cincuentazo" game.
Main
Main entry point for the Cincuentazo game application.
Player
Represents a player (human or machine) in the "Cincuentazo" game.
